    20→ *
    21→ * Endpoints:
    22→ *   GET  /healthz                       – liveness probe
    23→ *   GET  /v1/palettes?limit&offset      – list palettes
    24→ *   POST /v1/palettes                   – create palette  (see struct Palette spec)
    25→ *   POST /graphql                       – GraphQL façade (accepts JSON: {query:""})
    26→ *
    27→ * Copyright (c) 2023-2024
    28→ */
